            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Slice the<strong> ciabatta rolls </strong>in half</p>\n<p>Spread the <strong>ciabatta base</strong> with the <strong>mustard ketchup</strong></p>\n<p>Add the <strong>shredded</strong> <strong>ham hock</strong> to the <strong>ciabatta base</strong>, and top with the <strong>cheddar cheese </strong>and add to a baking tray with the <strong>ciabatta lids</strong> (cut side up)</p>\n<p>Put the tray in the oven for 3-4 mins or until the cheese has melted</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1296.-step-5.n-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1296.-step-5.n-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1296.-step-5.n-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1296.-step-5.n-x1000.jpg",
